Class ActionBaseValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • xtc.tree.Node
      • xtc.parser.Element
        • xtc.parser.ValueElement
          • xtc.parser.ActionBaseValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Object>, InternalElement, Locatable

    public class ActionBaseValue
extends ValueElement
    Element to set the semantic value to the result of applying a list of actions. The actions are applied by invoking ParserBase.apply(Pair,Object) on the list and a seed value.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.11 $
